Per vincere di più bisognerà trovare il moltiplicatore, che arriva a offrirti fino a 20 volte la tua scommessa. Tutto ciò che devi fare è metterti comodo e lasciarti conquistare dalle magiche avventure di queste principesse, che sono Love, Star e Storm.

La grafica richiama in modo incredibile i colori e l’idea di Sailor Moon: i disegni rispettano bene i classici giapponesi e sono capaci di allietare il giocatore con le animazioni di gioco. Review:
 
Gameplay mechanics and features

Moon Princess is a 5-reel, 20-payline online slot game that offers betting range from 0.20 to 100 coins per spin. Wins can be achieved both vertically and horizontally with three or more symbols. The game comes with Wild symbols that can replace any other symbol except the Scatter. Three Princesses - Love, Star, and Storm, offer different features to help a player wins more. Princess Trinity appears when all three princesses are involved in a win. Additionally, the game comes with Girl Power Bonus Game which can be activated on a non-winning spin. Once triggered, the bonus game will help the player to achieve more winning symbols and combinations.

Princess characters and theme

Moon Princess features three beautiful Princeses - Love, Star, and Storm. The game has been created with an amazing Japanese anime style to offer the player an immersive experience to remember. The graphics quality is top-notch, with illustrations that are reminiscent of the classic Sailor Moon anime. The aim with Moon Princess was to create a feminine aura around the game's characters, with each princess having a unique power to boost the player's chance of winning.

Coin prizes and multipliers

Moon Princess slot comes with a maximum win of up to 5,000 coins. This is achieved by getting the highest-paying symbols perfectly aligned on the paylines. The game further includes multipliers of up to 20 times your bet, which can boost your wins substantially. When a Wild symbol is included in the winning symbol combination, you can achieve a 5x multiplier on your bet. Additionally, if you clear the board of all the symbols, you may receive a prize of up to 100 times the bet made.

Availability on desktop and mobile devices

The Play N Go team made sure Moon Princess can be accessed on any mobile device or desktop. It offers the same seamless gameplay and graphics quality on any screen size, making it easy to play the game regardless of your device. Whether playing on a desktop, tablet or mobile phone, the game plays without any lags, offering a smooth experience all along. Players can access the game either through a mobile app or web browser.

Chance or skill-based bonus games

Moon Princess Slot appoints a chance-based bonus game named Girl Power. Players get a chance to enter the bonus game every time they have a non-winning spin. The bonus game is assigned to one of the three princesses. Depending on the princess, you have different opportunities to boost your chance of winning. Therefore, the bonus game comes as a great asset to help players succeed in obtaining significant wins from their gameplay.

Review: Moon Princess
You may think that the name of this slot game refers to a famous cartoon that was popular on Italian TV in the 90s: Have you ever heard of Sailor Moon? Well, even though it's not the official game, the online slot machine Moon Princess is the stellar game you've been looking for. The protagonists of this title are princesses in the perfect Japanese anime style, ready to give away free spins and prizes of up to 5,000 coins. To win more, you'll need to find the multiplier, which can offer up to 20 times your bet. All you have to do is get comfortable and let yourself be enchanted by the magical adventures of these princesses, who are Love, Star, and Storm.

Graphics and game symbols
The graphics incredibly evoke the colors and idea of Sailor Moon: the drawings do well to respect the classic Japanese style and delight the player with game animations. Moon Princess has 5 reels and 20 paylines, on which you can bet from 0.20 to 100 coins per spin. It is highly volatile and important wins can be obtained with 3 or more symbols in a row, both vertically and horizontally aligned. Whenever you achieve a winning combination, the symbols that form it will be eliminated, making room for new possible winning icons. In the center of a combination, a symbol of the Moon will then appear, which is the slot's Wild and allows us to replace any icon, as well as transform your bet up to 50 times with a 5x multiplier.

The Girl Power bonus game can be activated at random on a spin that is not winning. Depending on the princess that appears, there are different functions that favor the union of winning symbols. In the case of the Love Princess, you can choose 1 set of symbols that are transformed. With the Star Princess, you will have 1 or 2 Wilds added to your game board. And finally, with the Storm Princess, you can rely on 2 sets of symbols removed from the grid. But let's not forget the role of Trinity, the princess that arrives when wins are achieved only with the princesses: her purpose is to award a number of free spins. If the player manages to eliminate all the symbols, then the Free Spin function is activated, which varies depending on the princess. Also, by clearing the game board, you can receive a prize of up to 100 times the bet made.

Final thoughts on the Moon Princess slot
It is really worth trying out this fascinating slot machine that has been created by the software house Play N Go. Its success has allowed it to be made available on any mobile device or desktop. It does not lose anything in terms of gameplay and graphics even on smaller screens. The game is highly volatile (10/10) and has a default RTP of 96.50%. It manages to differentiate itself from the many titles present in the online gambling sector thanks to its amazing new features. These three princesses of great beauty and radiant smiles are ready to challenge you!
